OL,3,CEngland's Red Roses celebrate fifth
OL,4,CGrand Slam after defeating France
OL,6,FThe Red Roses have clinched their
OL,7,Ffifth successive Grand Slam, with
OL,8,FEllie Kildunne and Jess Breach running
OL,9,Fin two tries each in a 43-28 triumph
OL,10,Fover France in Bordeaux.
OL,12,FHot on the heels of last year's World
OL,13,FCup triumph, England secured their
OL,14,Feighth consecutive Guinness Women's
OL,15,FSix Nations title while extending
OL,16,Ftheir winning run to 38 Tests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
