OL,3,CEngland's Red Roses celebrate fifth
OL,4,CGrand Slam after defeating France
OL,6,FMeg Jones' team had to fight for their
OL,7,Fvictory, with France ` inspired by
OL,8,Ftheir dynamic scrum-half Pauline
OL,9,FBourdon Sansus ` threatening to reel
OL,10,Fthem in during the third quarter.
OL,12,FBut Breach's second try slammed the
OL,13,Fdoor on the comeback, and England
OL,14,Ffinished strongly as they once again
OL,15,Fovercame the absence of several World
OL,16,FCup players to injury and pregnancy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
