OL,3,CEngland's Red Roses celebrate fifth
OL,4,CGrand Slam after defeating France
OL,6,FEngland settled when Sarah Bern
OL,7,Fburrowed over from close range after a
OL,8,Fspell of pressure from their pack and
OL,9,Fthey then seized full control with
OL,10,FKildunne striking twice.
OL,12,FThe 2024 world player of the year had
OL,13,Frecovered from a heavy challenge that
OL,14,Fmight have been late and was first to
OL,15,Fthe ball when Jones fly-hacked ahead
OL,16,Fas the Red Roses reacted quickly to
OL,17,FFrance's attack breaking down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
