OL,3,CEngland's Red Roses celebrate fifth
OL,4,CGrand Slam after defeating France
OL,6,FA line-out move produced a late try
OL,7,Ffor Amy Cokayne to drive the visitors
OL,8,Ffurther ahead and, although Rose
OL,9,FBernadou crossed in overtime for
OL,10,FFrance, the final scoreline underlined
OL,11,FEngland's dominance of the women's
OL,12,Fgame.
